def: An East Indian carnivorous mammal (Prionodon gracilis),resembling the civets, but without scent pouches. It is handsomelyspotted.
A pulling; a disturbance. [Prov. Eng.] Halliwell.
To make clean by wiping; to wipe away; to cleanse; hence, topurge. [R.] Quincy.
Pertaining to a fascicle; fascicled; as, a fascicular root.
One who makes complaint; the plaintiff. [Obs.]
A generator having its revolving part carried on the shaft ofthe driving engine.
Pert. to or designating any form of spark tube the electricdischarge within which is used in spectroscopic observations.
The act by which falsehood and forgery are proved; an actionbrought for the purpose of having some instrument declared false orforged. Bell.
State of being heathen or like the heathen.
